333
00:23:58,850 --> 00:23:59,768
Xong.

334
00:23:59,768 --> 00:24:01,394
<i>Tôi làm khách mời dẫn show</i> Jeopardy!

335
00:24:01,811 --> 00:24:03,480
<i>Quảng cáo phấn rôm.</i>

336
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:05,440
